    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo describes the RTCP Payload-Specific Feedback Message Layer Refresh Request (LRR), which can be used to request a state refresh of one or more substreams of a layered media stream.  This document also defines its use with several RTP payloads for scalable media formats.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
